description:
Want to know what's on Player Attack this week? Well, here you go - a quick look at what you can expect from the next episode of Australia's newest video games TV series!

We go back to the movies for a quick disaster porn fix with San Andreas - if you go in expecting much more than The Rock vs The Earthquake, you'll probably be disappointed. (That's not a spoiler, right?)

Jackson spends some time with Nintendo's latest strategy release, Code Name S.T.E.A.M., and I try to figure out why everybody seems to have missed the absolute gem that is Marvel Heroes 2015.

Plus, of course, we have all the latest gaming news - this is Player Attack!
